definitions.definition: Any of the sharks in the family Scyliorhinidae
A deepwater catshark (any of family Pentanchidae ).
A coloured catshark (any of family Atelomycteridae ).
Any of several sharks of the family Pseudotriakidae .
A finback catshark (any of the family Proscylliidae ).
